ji\" />"},{"pid":"926b1882f2a8b47e25bd4fe3ee76e7ab292bbae2","tid":454992,"uid":92779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實收費點計？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常都係同附近D餐廳合作<br />\n山林道個度好似係60蚊 3個鍾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n山林道成班mk守住<br />\n唔幫襯必抄</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔幫襯你拎得番部車再講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6bbf7b32e8c013fe7e9592c86a69932933ebb29","tid":454992,"uid":92779,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:06:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實收費點計？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常都係同附近D餐廳合作<br />\n山林道個度好似係60蚊 3個鍾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁係直接比錢泊車仔先 定餐廳食完比？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n落車，同佢地講你去邊食飯，佢會幫你&quot;TUN&quot;個位出黎，幫我泊正係我食飯個間野門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過問心個句，比部車人揸就真係少少難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83cafe371de1615912c4fce99653d2a207140436","tid":454992,"uid":32028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:11:09.000Z","msg":"去呢d地方, 一係泊老遠, 一係唔去個區食, 再唔係就唔渣車"}]}